<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 版权：copyright&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> (四)class的命名:&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> (1)标题栏样式,使用"类别+功能"的方式命名,如&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> .barNews&nbsp;{&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> .barProduct&nbsp;{&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> (2)模块结构css定议&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 模块标题&nbsp;.module&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 模块标题&nbsp;.moduleHead&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 模块包装&nbsp;.moduleWrap&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 模块内容&nbsp;.moduleContent&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 注意事项:&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 1.一律小写;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 2.尽量用英文;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 3.不加中杠和下划线;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 4.尽量不缩写，除非一看就明白的单词.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 主要的&nbsp;master.css&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:13px;line-height:23.4px;"> 模块&nbsp;module.css&nbsp;